---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

---
<Base
  title="About us | EverCheck - CGM Manufacturer"
  description="EverCheck is a vertically integrated CGM manufacturer from China, specializing in biosensing technologies, scalable manufacturing, and flexible B2B partnerships."
>


<!-- NAV -->


<!-- HERO -->
<section class="about-us-hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" role="img" aria-label="EverCheck manufacturing facility and R&D center building exterior"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h1>A vertically integrated CGM manufacturer from China</h1>
      <p>Power your healthcare business with reliable CGM technologies, scalable manufacturing infrastructure, and flexible commercialization models tailored to regional healthcare markets. Start developing reliable glucose monitoring solutions more efficiently.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO ARE WE? -->
<section class="section" id="who-we-are">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row row-reverse">
      <div class="img-col">
        <div class="row-visual">
          <img src="/1.jpg" alt="EverCheck biosensing technology research and development facility">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-col">
        <div class="row-content">
          <h2>Who are we?</h2>
          <p>Founded in 2016, we specialize in the research, development, and commercialization of electrochemical biosensing technologies and biomolecular signal processing systems. Built on self-developed sensor chips, biosensors, and algorithm platforms, we have established integrated capabilities spanning from foundational technologies to end-user healthcare products. Our infrastructure includes Class&nbsp;10,000 cleanrooms, biosynthesis laboratories, and medical device assembly workshops &mdash; all under one roof for integrated in-house R&amp;D and scalable manufacturing.</p>
          <p>Today, our continuous glucose monitoring technologies are built exclusively for OEM, SKD, and many other types of healthcare commercialization partnerships across regional healthcare markets worldwide.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LEADERSHIP & SCIENTIFIC FOUNDATION -->
<section class="leadership-section" id="leadership">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Our leadership &amp; scientific foundation</h2>
      <p>A research-driven team guided by one of the most published scientists in electrochemical biosensing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="leadership-row">
      <div class="leadership-photo-wrap">
        <div class="leadership-photo-bg"></div>
        <img src="/x-zhang-transparent.png" alt="Professor Xueji Zhang" class="leadership-photo">
      </div>
      <div class="leadership-content">
        <h2>Prof. Xueji Zhang</h2>
        <p class="role">Chief Scientist &amp; Co-founder</p>
        <p>Professor Xueji Zhang is a world-renowned scientist in the field of biosensing and electrochemical analysis. With decades of research experience spanning sensor design, biomolecular detection, and clinical diagnostics, he has been instrumental in establishing EverCheck's core technology platform from the ground up.</p>
        <p>His research bridges fundamental science and practical healthcare applications, driving the development of high-accuracy glucose monitoring systems that meet rigorous clinical standards.</p>
        <div class="credentials">
          <h4>Key credentials</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Fellow of the Royal Society of Chemistry (FRSC)</li>
            <li>Extensive publication record in top-tier journals on biosensing and electrochemistry</li>
            <li>Deep expertise in enzyme-based sensor design and clinical diagnostic technologies</li>
            <li>Led multiple national research programs in biomedical engineering and sensor development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MILESTONES -->
<section class="milestones-section" id="milestones">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Our milestones</h2>
      <p>From early-stage biosensor R&amp;D to commercial-scale CGM manufacturing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-year">2016</span><span class="timeline-label">Concept validation</span>
        <p>Founded and started R&amp;D on proprietary sensor chips and biosensors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-year">2017&mdash;019</span><span class="timeline-label">Pre-product development</span>
        <p>Prof. Xueji Zhang appointed as Chairman &amp; Chief Scientist. Obtained National High-Tech Enterprise certification.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-year">2020&mdash;021</span><span class="timeline-label">Product launch</span>
        <p>Completed first-generation CGM prototype.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-year">2022</span><span class="timeline-label">System finalization</span>
        <p>CGM system design finalized; cleanroom completed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-year">2023&mdash;024</span><span class="timeline-label">Commercialization &amp; scale</span>
        <p>CGM automated production line launched. Mass production of CGM achieved. R&amp;D product line fully iterated and achieved scaled sales.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CORE TECHNOLOGIES -->
<section class="section section-alt" id="technologies">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Our core technologies</h2>
      <p>Six technology pillars built and controlled in house, covering the full journey from sensor chip to finished CGM device.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Chip / CPU icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="6" y="6" width="12" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M9 6V3M15 6V3M9 18v3M15 18v3M6 9H3M6 15H3M18 9h3M18 15h3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Proprietary sensor chips</h4>
        <p>We design and fabricate our own electrochemical sensor chips in-house. This gives us direct control over signal stability, power consumption, and form factor. It also removes dependency on third-party semiconductor supply chains.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Flask / Biosensing icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 3h6M10 3v7l-5 9h14l-5-9V3"/><path d="M7 15h10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Enzyme-based biosensing</h4>
        <p>Our glucose oxidase sensors are formulated, coated, and calibrated internally. Batch-level MARD validation ensures consistent accuracy across every production run, not just the reference batch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Code / Algorithm icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Self-developed algorithms</h4>
        <p>We build our own glucose calculation, trend prediction, and alert logic from the ground up. This lets us customize for pediatric ranges, gestational thresholds, or insulin pump communication protocols without waiting on external roadmap priorities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Layers / Biochemical icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"/><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"/><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Biochemical processing platform</h4>
        <p>Enzyme immobilization, membrane deposition, and sensitivity tuning are handled under one roof. Controlling these steps internally is what lets us maintain sub-8% MARD consistency at scale.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Factory / Manufacturing icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2 20h20M5 20v-8l5 4V8l5 4V4l5 4v12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Integrated manufacturing</h4>
        <p>From biosensor wafer to sealed transmitter, every stage happens in our own facilities. Each unit gets a unique QR code for full component traceability, and automated in-line testing catches deviations before they leave the line.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Check-circle / Inspection icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>SPC-controlled quality systems</h4>
        <p>We run Statistical Process Control across electrode printing, laser cutting, dispensing, and coating. Our own inspection equipment feeds data back into the line in real time, so we adjust before defects accumulate, not after.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section" id="drives">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>What drives us forward?</h2>
      <p>The vision, mission, and values that guide every decision we make, from sensor design to partner relationships.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="drives-grid">
      <div class="drive-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Eye / Vision icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Our vision</h4>
        <p>To become a world-leading provider of biosensing systems and healthcare technologies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="drive-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Target / Mission icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Our mission</h4>
        <p>To support healthcare businesses with reliable biosensing technologies and scalable commercialization infrastructure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="drive-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <!-- Shield / Values icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Values</h4>
        <p>We believe in staying low-profile, working pragmatically, and advancing steadily through efficient execution and long-term technological commitment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER CTA -->
<section class="section" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-cta">
      <h2>Your long-term B2B CGM manufacturing partner</h2>
      <p>We combine self-developed CGM technologies with scalable manufacturing infrastructure to support healthcare brands worldwide.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact us now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

</Base>
